## E-Commerce Sales Analysis (2022â€“2024)

This project explores three years of e-commerce sales data to assess overall business performance, profitability trends, product category results, and regional contributions.

The goal of the analysis is to:
- Identify year-over-year growth patterns  
- Detect performance declines  
- Evaluate profit margins  
- Determine the main revenue drivers across categories and regions  

The insights generated from this analysis help support data-driven decision-making and highlight areas for potential strategic improvement.
